<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/85825923-ivanopinion"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_100x100-c7bfe730633c9983e27caaa66a8e244a.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/85825923-ivanopinion">IvanOpinion</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think it was that such an orbit would be within Hermian &quot;jurisdiction&quot;, so they felt more able to assert their view that malign intentions should be<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think it was that such an orbit would be within Hermian "jurisdiction", so they felt more able to assert their view that malign intentions should be assumed. <br /><br />(Given the level of Raman technology, I'm pretty sure that Rama would have had self-defence capabilities easily able to foil a nuclear missile. I rather expected the plot would develop with the missile being detonated and having no effect or Rama's defences splatting the missile seconds before detonation.)<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
